name: WAGMI With Wagyu
description:
An Aged and Curated A.I. Collection by Tiv

Same old powdered cricket extract getting you down? Does buying yet another copy in a slurry of derivatives feel like a huge mis-steak? 
Worried that in five years your low ordinals inscription will be just another MoonCat... or worse? 

Fill your emptiness with some marbled madness.

WAGMI With Wagyu. 
125 Dreams of Electric Meat from me to you
